@startuml sequence_gitignore_check
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Gitignore Protection Check (Check-Gitignore.ps1)

actor Candidate
participant "Check-Gitignore.ps1" as Script
participant "Git" as Git
participant ".gitignore" as Gitignore

Candidate -> Script : Invoke Check-Gitignore.ps1

Script -> Git : Run: git status --porcelain
Git --> Script : Return tracked/untracked file list

Script -> Gitignore : Read protected path patterns
Gitignore --> Script : Return pattern list:\n data/pipeline.md\n data/scan-history.tsv\n data/search-results/\n content/evaluations/\n content/outreach/\n *.env\n config/profile.yml

Script -> Script : Scan git status output\nfor any protected path pattern match

alt No violations found
    Script --> Candidate : All protected paths are excluded.\nNo action required.
else Violations found
    Script --> Candidate : VIOLATIONS DETECTED:\n[list of matched paths]\nAction: add paths to .gitignore\nor remove from tracking\n(git rm --cached <path>)
end

@enduml
